// tryRotate.bps — Demo of _rotate() tool
// Traduit de bp3-engine/test-data/-gr.tryRotate (Bernard, 1998)

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:midi

@mode:random
S -> ![/6] {![rotate:K1=2] M} 1/2 N
N -> N ![rotate:K1] {N 1/2} [weight:5-1]

-----

@mode:random
M -> C4 D4 E4 F4 G4
N -> C5 D5 E5 F5 G5 A5 B5 C6 D6 E6
